{"tid":449602,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone X 訂單狂被 Cut？方保僑怒斥：衰過大陸公司","createTime":"2017-10-27T10:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T03:17:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":14,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"be9f769fd66a6f5430dd85011d64f7e7086c0cf4","tid":449602,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1930000/1934327/fong_01_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1930000%2F1934327%2Ffong_01_1024.jpg&h=1021a33d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\niPhone X 今日開放預購，雖然經 iReserve 較難預留 iPhone X，但經 AOS 網購 iPhone X 則相對較易。科技界 KOL、香港資訊科技商會榮譽會長方保僑（Francis；下圖）今日都成功經《Apple Store》官方 App 訂購 2 部 iPhone X，卻在下午 5 時多，發現自己的 iPhone X 訂單已被 cut 單！<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=17877b53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 聯絡到 Francis，他直斥蘋果公司的 cut 單做法「仲衰過大陸公司」。<br />\n<br />\n方保僑約於下午 5 時多，於其個人 Facebook 帳戶出 post 透露被 cut 單。<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=17877b53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 隨即聯絡當事人，Francis 表示自己經《Apple Store》App 訂了 2 部 iPhone X，原本直接用 Apple Pay 支付，惟當時程式指出有問題，遂改為輸入 HSBC 信用卡資料進行交易；成功付款後，他一直不為意，直至約 5 時收到朋友通知，表示 iPhone X 訂單被蘋果公司取消了，才檢查電郵，一查便看到蘋果公司傳來的電郵。電郵中指出，無法取得信用卡的授權，因此無法繼續訂單，要求轉用另一張信用卡或更改付款方式。<br />\n<br />\n方氏之後致電蘋果公司客戶服務熱線，輸入訂單號碼後，一直聯絡不上任何客戶服務員，他怒斥蘋果公司：「咁大間公司，都可以咁樣取消訂單，電話又無人接聽，我覺得做法連大陸公司都不如！」他估計，蘋果公司根本沒有這麼多 iPhone X 存貨，但由於 payment gateway 應付不了龐大的訂單量，於是先行接受大量訂單，再慢慢 cut 單。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，<a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=17877b53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a> 的 Facebook 官方專頁都有收到讀者的訊號，指出訂了 iPhone X 之後，收到蘋果公司的 cut 單通知。暫時無法估計蘋果公司 cut 單的原因，訂了機的你，最好還是檢查一下 Apple 帳戶或電郵吧！"},{"pid":"6b0e5236d743f3ea9cfd01bb3f26a6620caba21e","tid":449602,"uid":759,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"就係大間先敢cut你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8487ebbc5b0977e2d9d2c896856e2967eb279f15","tid":449602,"uid":63,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"等下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4d5d05d6a2444ff0aae0c7b043dfdde16b4e29","tid":449602,"uid":79563,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"咁你訂小米囉<br />\n<br />\n乜野方保僑?<br />\n<br />\n識你係老鼠"},{"pid":"5b3d6e9cde8b8b5ef33bad9daf60b5ca187e228f","tid":449602,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"hsbc都cut!?"},{"pid":"af49cc0ff9be73ff9b25da106fb6ef908089d372","tid":449602,"uid":36049,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:35:33.000Z","msg":"哪誰呀,講到自己有特權咁🤣😂😂"},{"pid":"f4e7ecd8a3e14e71a63374dac83bbe6cd7bc9d96","tid":449602,"uid":13718,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"收皮啦KOL <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38763eae495bcf9dfdedac294e046f0ee74a6692","tid":449602,"uid":20815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"張卡有問題呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋點解要人通知先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faf1a96ff9744448ea8ca989d74b47c03fc0d14","tid":449602,"uid":23993,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"哎喲喲<br />\n比蘋果cut單嬲嬲